title: Vlog | @nikiivictoria
description: Spend a day with me living in NYC

subtitles.text: the first thing I try to do every morning is meditate
subtitles.translation: 아침에 제일 먼저 하려고 하는 건 명상이야.

subtitles.text: or yoga I made this priority
subtitles.translation: 아니면 요가. 요즘은 이걸 우선순위로 두고 있거든.

subtitles.text: of course coffee is a priority as well
subtitles.translation: 물론 커피도 내겐 아주 중요한 일이야.

subtitles.text: you could see I'm a coffee addict

subtitles.translation: 그다음엔 아침 챙겨 먹고, 비타민 먹고

subtitles.text: and then I start getting ready for the day
this morning I had a personal training session at my gym
subtitles.translation: 오늘 아침엔 헬스장에서 PT 받는 날이라

subtitles.text: so I did some very light skincare
